- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving accuracy and convergence rates of neural sequence predictors. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a less likely category, but it is mentioned that the proposed method performs well for image captioning tasks. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a less likely category, but it is relevant as the paper proposes a technique to mitigate exposure bias in training neural sequence predictors.
